    'missions.section1.cards.card1.text1' => 'Keep a constant',
    'missions.section1.cards.card1.text2' => 'watch',
    'missions.section1.cards.card1.description' => 'Since its establishment in 1995, ONDE has had a priority mission: the continuous monitoring of the situation of children in Morocco and the evaluation of actions undertaken in all areas relating to the well-being of this category of the population.',
    'missions.section1.cards.card2.text1' => 'Inform the public and',
    'missions.section1.cards.card2.text2' => 'raise awareness',
    'missions.section1.cards.card2.description' => 'A child who fully enjoys his or her rights is a child who lives in a society that is aware and conscious of the issues of respect for children. It is with this in mind that ONDE carries out activities aimed at informing, raising awareness and advising the various bodies concerned with the protection and promotion of children\'s rights.',
    'missions.section1.cards.card3.text1' => 'Demonstrative actions in favor',
    'missions.section1.cards.card3.text2' => 'of the child',
    'missions.section1.cards.card3.description' => 'To ensure full effectiveness, ONDE undertakes demonstrative actions to promote the rights of the child in the areas of health, education, justice, culture, etc.',
    'missions.section1.cards.card4.text1' => 'Federate and guide',
    'missions.section1.cards.card4.text2' => 'Public policy',
    'missions.section1.cards.card4.description' => 'ONDE plays the role of federator. It is responsible for coordinating intersectional initiatives undertaken by national and international partners in favor of children.',
